This project aims to perform various kinds of analysis on twitter feeds.
1: Real time analysis on any topic/person/hashtag.
2: Batch mode analysis on any topic/person/hashtag.
3: Sentiment analysis of tweets. (by topic/person/hashtag)


Note: Since, we're not allowed to store twitter data for more than 24 hours, all the batch-mode operations will have a window of 24 hours only.

